reviewText: a lot of discs for this show and I think it's not done yet so hope there is more to come.
item came on time in excellent condition great service hope I can do business with this seller again highly recommended!

Zatch Bell is one of those forgotten anime's that use to air on the cartoon network a few years ago. I'm happy to report that Zatch Bell is as fun as ever. The series is silly, often times ridiculous but a lot of fun. Watch Zatch Bell when you're not felling so grown up and serious and just enjoy.

This is not the complete series.
